# docs/ site build artifacts (docs/package.json is a separate dependency tree — see AGENTS.md).
# docs/.vitepress/dist is already covered by the "dist/" pattern above. This pattern contains an
# internal "/" so, per gitignore semantics, it is rooted relative to this file's directory (repo
